values.value: PAYMENT FOR THIS SERVICE IS DENIED. OUR RECORDS SHOW YOU HAVE COVERAGE WITH MEDICARE. PLEASE SEND US A COPY OF THE MEDICARE EXPLANATION OF BENEFITS (MEOB) THAT MATCHES ALL SERVICES ON THIS CLAIM. CHECK WITH YOUR PROVIDER TO SEE IF THE MEOB HAS ALREADY BEEN SENT TO US. IF NOT, SEND THE MEOB ALONG WITH THIS EXPLANATION OF BENEFITS TO THE RETURN ADDRESS SHOWN ABOVE.
